président <colour id="3" />Tom Nook<colour id="65535" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /> on a appelé cet endroit<anim id="BigSmile" target="4" targetSpec="N2" /> <colour id="1" />Boutique
Nook<colour id="65535" />!</message>
